{
  "texts": [
    "• Stemming: Words were reduced to their root form to group different variations of the same word.",
    "• Lemmatization: Words were converted to their base form to capture their core meaning.• Removing special characters: Special characters were removed to improve the readability of the dataset.",
    "• Missing values: For papers lacking specific authors' keywords, indexed keywords supplied by the Elsevier Scopus API (Elsevier 2022) were used as substitutes.",
    "• Misspelled words correction: Some papers contained misspelled keywords, like \"anonimisation.\"",
    "To address this problem, we developed Python scripts to identify keywords with the most similar spelling and replace the incorrect ones."
  ]
}